ange of points you want. The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"location"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"first point you are requesting, with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" being the first point, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":" being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the second point, and so on. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"length"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates the number of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points you want. The array in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coords"}]},{"type":"text","text":" must be large enough to accommodate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the number of requested coordinates."}]}],"name":"range"}],"kind":"parameters"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Retrieves one or more coordinates associated with the shape.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection\/getCoordinates:range:"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection/getCoordinates:range:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection\/getCoordinates:range:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection\/getcoordinates:range:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getCoordinates:range:"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"getCoordinates:range:","abstract":[{"text":"Retrieves